00:26:42.730 --> 00:26:45.430
The way this works is there is a
windowing system in Android,

00:26:45.430 --> 00:26:48.430
just like there is in any other
modern operating system.

00:26:48.430 --> 00:26:53.180
You don't really use it very
often because everything's

00:26:53.180 --> 00:26:54.550
