But in this case, what we have
is a view here that's going to

00:27:00.630 --> 00:27:03.920
actually get a hole
punched it.

00:27:03.920 --> 00:27:05.370
In other words, part of it's
going to be transparent and

00:27:05.370 --> 00:27:07.320
there's going to be a window
underneath it, which is

00:27:07.320 --> 00:27:09.350
actually showing the map.

00:27:09.350 --> 00:27:13.960
Now this area here is being
drawn in a second context.

