00:27:32.800 --> 00:27:41.610
Next thing that's going to get
drawn is the actual overlay.

00:27:41.610 --> 00:27:43.800
This is what made
me intrigued.

00:27:43.800 --> 00:27:47.080
Because if you look at some
of these, you can see that

00:27:47.080 --> 00:27:49.690
there's some interesting
artifacts that are basically

00:27:49.690 --> 00:27:52.050
