is slightly wrong.

00:28:21.530 --> 00:28:25.660
We're doing a per vertex text
chord into this essentially

00:28:25.660 --> 00:28:29.410
one-dimensional texture that
takes us all away from the

00:28:29.410 --> 00:28:31.600
